object.doc: The root class for most of the model classes.

object.attribute: String.Format('{0}:{1} ({2}/{3} {4})', self.DocumentType, self.DocumentNr, self.PaidGrossValue, self.DocumentGrossValue, self.DocumentCurr)
if(self.DocumentBelongsToPayer) then 0-PaidGrossValue else if(self.DocumentBelongsToPayee) then PaidGrossValue else 0 endif endif
if(self.DocumentBelongsToPayer) then 0-DocumentGrossValue else if(self.DocumentBelongsToPayee) then DocumentGrossValue else 0 endif endif
